skin is the largest organ of the body, and it can be an amazing diversity of types: skin (normal soft skin which can be torn bloody by 'rope burn' or super hard~tough callous skin which can handle 'rope burn' without any damage, fur, feathers, and scales. These are all the different forms that the skin organ can become, so cool, hehe! ( <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skin">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Skin</a><!-- m --> )

similiarly is hair: from hair to rhino tusks~horn~whatever to fingernails, that is the range of hair diversity!

